description: Try our easy to follow Moroccan Beef, Pumpkin & Couscous Filo Pie recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Moroccan Beef, Pumpkin & Couscous Filo Pie
name: Moroccan Beef, Pumpkin & Couscous Filo Pie Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Pile beef filling mixture into centre. Fold overhanging pastry over the top of filling. Spray with olive oil. Bake for 20-25 minutes or until pastry is golden brown and crisp all over. Cut into wedges and serve with yoghurt.
